msgstr ""

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:376
msgid "Warning: There are unsaved changes that will get lost on reboot!"
msgstr "Προσοχή: Οι μη αποθηκευμένες αλλαγές θα χαθούν με την επανεκκίνηση!"

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:481
